      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Larry_Coryell_1979.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/Larry_Coryell_1979.jpg/330px-Larry_Coryell_1979.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"454\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/34/Larry_Coryell_1979.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Larry_Coryell_1979.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Larry Coryell, 1979 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larry_Coryell\">Larry Coryell</a>, (April 2, 1943 – February 19, 2017)<br />\nwas an American jazz guitarist.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:Larry_Coryell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Larry Coryell at Bach Dancing&amp;Dynamite Society, Half Moon Bay CA 1979. Photo: Brian McMillen / brianmcmillen@hotmail.com</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301030735\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.086 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.632 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 21/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 58/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function coun